'''7. Assuming that we have some email addresses in the 
"username@companyname.com" format, write a program to print the company 
name of a given email address. Both user names and company names are 
composed of letters only. '''

mail=input("Enter mail:")

i1=mail.index("@")
i2=mail.index(".com")

print("Company name:",mail[i1+1:i2])
